1 opportunities for children; afterwards, they become part of the organization's alumni
2 network, and in Louisiana, there are alumni in more than thirty parishes; and
3 WHEREAS, Teach For America also provides a high-impact tutoring program called
4 the Ignite Fellowship, which recruits and trains college students to provide in-school virtual
5 high dosage tutoring for students who need additional support in literacy; there are over four
6 hundred thirty Ignite Fellowship high dosage tutors in Louisiana; and
7 WHEREAS, Teach For America and its members are most deserving of the highest
8 recognition for their dedicated efforts to create educational opportunity for all students,
9 thereby laying the foundation for a better future for American education.
10 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
11 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Teach For America for its efforts to improve
12 educational outcomes in Louisiana and throughout the country and does hereby extend
13 sincerest wishes that the organization and its members continue to prosper in their endeavors
14 to improve American education.
